{"tid":1969739,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森 討論區 (155)","createTime":"2020-04-12T15:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T16:52:54.000Z","uid":353380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35ba916eec569abadfc047aa09af8ef8c76a10fb","tid":1969739,"uid":353380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1001開post時希望可以copy埋置頂</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">(用右上三點可以此內容開新post, 可以的話copy埋 置頂嗰堆)</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">置頂</span></strong>有遊戲初期常見問題/實用工具/秘技<br />\n<br />\n <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">參觀人哋個島必讀 &mdash;&mdash; 良好島民約章</span></strong><br />\n1. 未經同意唔好走去搖人哋棵樹／執人啲野<br />\n2. 跑步注意安全，唔好踩爛人哋啲花<br />\n3. 個袋滿左之後，唔好周地dump垃圾<br />\n4. 唔好偷人啲野，「摸」完野記得要還<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">買game前你可能會想知 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：隻game玩乜？<br />\nA：比較休閒嘅第二人生。隻game時間係跟現實時間，亦慶祝現實節日例如聖誕，復活節等等。遊戲著重你同動物森民嘅交流互動(隻隻都有自己性格)，慢慢一齊生活 了解對方 成為密友， 同埋裝飾你間屋＆島。今隻主題係無人荒島，亦新增合成元素，你要由零開始<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">還債</span></span></del>建設你心目中嘅理想小島。遊戲節奏比較輕鬆，預你日日開來玩一陣，啱玩嘅可以玩幾年都得。<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩版先有中文？唔同版本可唔可以連機？<br />\nA：乜版都有中文 。可以<br />\n<br />\nQ：Online 玩咩？<br />\nA：你可以去朋友／網友嘅島度一齊開party，一齊hea，一齊砌野，一齊炒<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">股票</span></span></del>蘿蔔。<br />\n<br />\nQ：單機會唔會無咁好玩？<br />\nA：唔會，隻game係單機game，主要都係著重起你同動物之間嘅交流互動同埋打理你座島。不過多人連機時一樣有野玩咁解。<br />\n<br />\nQ：對手掣好靚，有無得單買？<br />\nA：暫時只見日本My Nintendo Store有得買，但係<del>唔收香港卡</del>同唔寄香港。 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">更新: 原來已更新可以用PayPal俾錢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：可唔可以用返以前啲Amiibo ＆ Amiibo Card？<br />\nA：可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFWQrY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFWQrY.png&h=8c46d7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">圖片來源 YouTube -&gt; rEB1vlAiVxE</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nQ：買game實體定下載版好？有無黃店推介？<br />\nA：隻game預你日日開來玩一陣 實係下載版好，仲唔怕會益代理，真係怕唔啱玩要買實體我會建議你幫襯黃店買水貨。Read: 黃藍黑Game舖大集合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：同一部機唔同user save係共通？<br />\nA：無錯，一部機全部user都係住同一個島。<br />\n<br />\nQ：一機多人玩係點？<br />\nA：只有1P可以推展遊戲進度，2P只係執下素材咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無Cloud Save？咁我壞機點算？<br />\nA：無。但官方講法係「Online會員專用壞機／唔見機時尋回save file功能開發中」 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好反智</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無得轉移個save去第二部機部度？<br />\nA：暫時無。官方講法係「動森專用 機對機save轉移功能開發中」<br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩動物村民？<br />\nA：今集總共有383個<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好似係</span></span>。全村民「圖鑑」未有，但根據歷作會有鱷魚／食蟻獸／熊／鳥／牛／貓／雞／鹿／狗／鴨／鷹／象／蛙／羊／倉鼠／河馬／猩猩／狼／虎／松鼠／犀牛／兔／豬／企鵝／八爪魚／鴕鳥／鼠／馬騮／獅子／袋鼠／樹熊／馬... 歷代全角色(好多頁): <a href=\"https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanimalcrossing.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3ACharacters&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2BExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=3efb4b89\" target=\"_blank\">https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">港版特別主機(電力加強版)</span></strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>※並非數量限定商品。日後將預定再次生產</strong></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">-(<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Ftopics%2Farticle%2Fa_200131_02.html&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2BExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=ab3b006d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html</a>)</span><br />\n預訂店鋪一覽: (官方頭盔: ※預訂及商品在庫狀況因店舖實際情況而異，詳情請向各店店員查詢)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fhardware%2Fswitch%2Fstore%2Fanimal.html&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2BExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=6ac2a972\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入手請幫襯UNY/APITA/AEON/豐澤</span></strong> (唔經代理拎貨)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/animal_crossing_new_horizons/set/img/img-main-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fanimal_crossing_new_horizons%2Fset%2Fimg%2Fimg-main-06.jpg&h=56e37b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">召集所有3DS版熟悉的面孔同新人一齊加入</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"bfff25a4d3f12a14f5f15d11ef2620829b0d086a","tid":1969739,"uid":353380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遊戲初期常見問題 // 實用online tools // <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n＞Android/iOS 「Nintendo Switch Online」app可以scan設計QR code，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">連機時可以快速打字傾計</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">遊戲初期常見問題Q&amp;A</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>(太長click入去睇-&gt;) </strong></span><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/kZjMuNXh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FkZjMuNXh&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2BExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=ff5df8bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/kZjMuNXh</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"