>\n<a href=\"https://tunes.nooknet.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftunes.nooknet.net%2F&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2BExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=77ff11ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://tunes.nooknet.net/</a><br />\n設計無人島<br />\n<a href=\"https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplanimalcrossing.com%2Fnh%2Fstart%2F&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2BExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=872278f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VW0LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VW0LS.png&h=a2e5c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQ：風水？<br />\nA：主人房擺唔同顏色家具增加運氣，綠 整體，紅 物品，黃 金錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/FRbfJgYp/fengshui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FFRbfJgYp%2Ffengshui.jpg&h=dc333a39&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thonky.com/animal-crossing-new-leaf/feng-shui-guide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thonky.com%2Fanimal-crossing-new-leaf%2Ffeng-shui-guide&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2BExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=abdb8afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thonky.com/animal-crossing-new-leaf/feng-shui-guide</a><br />\n<br />\nＱ：花係咪可以配種？<br />\nＡ：同類花種埋一齊，淋水，側邊有機會出新色花<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GL7F8T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GL7F8T.png&h=a012237e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nＱ：點拎多啲礦石？<br />\nＡ：好似幅圖咁整三個窿先<